据评论家称，这些是有史以来最恐怖的恐怖电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-are-the-scariest-horror-movies-ever-according-to-critics-3808786?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=these-are-the-scariest-影评人评价的恐怖电影Max PilleyFri, 01 Nov 2024 17:37:36 +0000 Film NewsNewsHorror https://www.nme.com/?p=3808786 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斯皮尔伯格" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>前 20 名包括上世纪电影界的经典之作</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-are-the-scariest-horror-movies-ever-according-to-critics-3808786">据评论家称，这是有史以来最恐怖的恐怖电影，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斯皮尔伯格" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jaws_poster-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>恐怖电影像其他类型的电影一样引发对话和辩论，但历史上收视率最高的恐怖电影是哪些？</p><p>评论聚合网站<a href="https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/best-horror-movies-of-all-time/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>烂番茄</i></a>整理了世界各地的评论共识，并汇总了该类型百年历史中最受好评的电影清单，该清单还将观众驱动的“爆米花计”纳入其方程式。</p><p>在这份充满 24 克拉经典之作的榜单中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steven-spielberg">史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格 (Steven Spielberg</a> ) 1975 年的大片《大白鲨<i>》 (Jaws)</i>占据了久负盛名的榜首位置。改编自彼得·本奇利的小说，它让一代电影观众感到恐惧，以致人们在上映后多年不敢去海滩游泳。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="大白鲨 |官方预告片|在 IMAX® 中体验" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WKuZJjPSLXQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>罗伊·谢德尔饰演的警察局长马丁·布罗迪在罗伯特·肖饰演的鲨鱼猎人的帮助下，追捕一只在阿米蒂岛海滩上捕食度假者的食人大白鲨。它成为典型的夏季大片，并成为有史以来票房最高的电影，但两年后被<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars"><i>《星球大战》</i></a>超越。</p><p>排在第二位的是瑞典吸血鬼电影《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/let-the-right-one-in-is-the-best-vampire-movie-of-all-time-47950"><i>让对的人进来</i></a>》，影评人评分为 98%，观众评分为 90%。托马斯·阿尔弗雷德森 (Tomas Alfredson) 执导了<i>《锅匠裁缝士兵间谍》</i> ，这部影片讲述了 20 世纪 80 年代初斯德哥尔摩一名受欺负的 12 岁男孩与一名神秘女孩建立了亲密友谊的故事。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="让合适的人出现在官方高清预告片中" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ICp4g9p_rgo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 2009 年英国上映时， <i>《NME》</i>宣称该片为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/let-the-right-one-in-is-the-best-vampire-movie-of-all-time-47950">有史以来最好的吸血鬼电影</a>”。</p><p>排在前三名的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ridley-scott">雷德利·斯科特 (Ridley Scott</a> ) 1979 年的科幻恐怖片《异形》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/alien"><i>(Alien)</i></a> ，获得了高达 93% 的影评人和 94% 的观众评分。这部电影让西格妮·韦弗 (Sigourney Weaver) 成为明星，并从 HR·吉格 (HR Giger) 的传奇生物设计和约翰·赫特 (John Hurt) 爆胸场景的口碑震撼中汲取了力量。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《异形》高清预告片（原版 1979 年雷德利·斯科特电影）西格妮·韦弗" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jQ5lPt9edzQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>榜单的其余部分展示了多代恐怖经典，从老式默片时代（ <i>《诺斯费拉图》</i> 、 <i>《卡里加里博士的内阁》</i> ），到当代的杰出作品，如<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jordan-peele">乔丹·皮尔</a>的《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/get-out-film-review-2018268"><i>逃出绝命</i></a>镇》和日本独立喜剧僵尸电影<i>《One》死者之切</i>。</p><p>仔细阅读下面完整的前 20 部影片，包括恐怖片、僵尸、连环杀手和怪物电影子类型的经典影片。</p><h2><b>烂番茄列出的史上 20 部最佳恐怖片名单是：</b> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="631" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b><i>大白鲨</i></b><b>(1975)</b> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="631" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b><i>让对的人进来</i></b><b>(2008)</b> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="631" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;4697