观看 Cyndi Lauper 在麦迪逊广场花园与 Sam Smith 演唱《Time After Time》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-cyndi-lauper-sing-time-after-time-with-sam-smith-at-madison-square-garden-3808749?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=观看辛迪·劳珀与萨姆·史密斯在麦迪逊广场花园一次又一次地唱歌Anagricel DuranFri, 01 Nov 2024 16:54:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3808749 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Cyndi Lauper 和 Sam Smith 于 2024 年 10 月 30 日在纽约市麦迪逊广场花园举行的 Cyndi Lauper 的《Girls Just Wanna Have Fun 告别巡演》中表演。 （泰勒·希尔/盖蒂图片社为 Live Nation 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>史密斯此前曾于 2021 年在 Abbey Road Studios 翻唱过这首歌</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-cyndi-lauper-sing-time-after-time-with-sam-smith-at-madison-square-garden-3808749">观看 Cyndi Lauper 与 Sam Smith 在麦迪逊广场花园演唱《Time After Time》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Cyndi Lauper 和 Sam Smith 于 2024 年 10 月 30 日在纽约市麦迪逊广场花园举行的 Cyndi Lauper 的《Girls Just Wanna Have Fun 告别巡演》中表演。 （泰勒·希尔/盖蒂图片社为 Live Nation 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cyndi-Lauper-and-Sam-Smith-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Cyndi-Lauper">辛迪·劳珀 (Cyndi Lauper)</a>与<a href="/artists/Sam-Smith">萨姆·史密斯 (Sam Smith)</a>在纽约麦迪逊广场花园合作合唱了《Time After Time》。</p><p>这位流行偶像于周三（10 月 30 日）接管了这个传奇场地，作为她“Girls Just Wanna Have Fun 告别巡演”的一部分。劳珀以她的热门歌曲“The Goonies &#39;R&#39; Good Enough”拉开了当晚的序幕，然后播放了她职业生涯中的唱片中的曲目。</p><p>在演出接近尾声时，劳珀演唱了《Time After Time》，并邀请史密斯作为惊喜嘉宾。 “Stay With Me”歌手出现在第二节。两人手牵着手，一边唱着这首歌一边跳舞。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Cyndi Lauper 与 Sam Smith - Time After Time - 于 2024 年 10 月 30 日在麦迪逊广场花园现场直播。" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qKLOa7SFNKg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Smith 曾于 2021 年在 Abbey Road Studios 翻唱过 Lauper 1984 年的热门单曲，作为他们专辑《Love Goes: Live At Abbey Road Studios》的一部分。 《Time After Time》作为流行偶像的首张唱片《She&#39;s So Unusual》发行。它达到了第一名的顶峰，并经常被认为是有史以来最好的歌曲之一。</p><p>这位“True Colors”歌手将于今晚（11 月 1 日）在田纳西州纳什维尔的普利司通体育场演出。她正在进行的告别巡演将持续到 12 月初，届时这位纽约歌手将在美国各地演出。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cyndi-lauper-announces-details-of-farewell-tour-3762181">请访问此处查看完整的旅游日期列表</a>，并点击<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fcyndi-lauper-tickets%2Fartist%2F735490" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。</p><p>早在六月，劳珀<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cyndi-lauper-explains-reasoning-behind-her-farewell-tour-3763466">就向吉米·坎摩尔讲述了这次巡演，并解释了为什么她觉得现在是最后一次长途跋涉的最佳时机</a>。</p><p>虽然劳珀澄清说她绝不会退休，但她排除了“火车、飞机和汽车”的可能性，这表明她对偶尔在家乡演出持开放态度。她进一步解释道：“我想做一场竞技场巡演……我现在很强大，但我不知道四年后我会是什么样子。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DB1YQ4bO0xy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39